          <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/devgandhi7/Callix-Research-/main/IMG_3656.jpg" alt="Placebo-Cued Medicine for Neurological Conditions">
          <h3 class="device-heading"><a href="https://www.callixresearch.com/innovations/placebo-cued-medicine">Placebo-Cued Medicine for Neurological Conditions</a></h3>
          <p>Our patented Placebo-Cued Medicine technology represents a breakthrough in treating conditions influenced by neural pathways—including depression, anxiety, pain, and sleep disorders—by incorporating distinct sensory cues that activate the body's natural therapeutic responses, potentially enhancing medication efficacy while reducing dependency.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/devgandhi7/Callix-Research-/main/IMG_3652.jpg" alt="Placebo-Cued Medicine for Pain Management">
          <h3 class="device-heading"><a href="https://www.callixresearch.com/innovations/placebo-cued-opiod">Placebo-Cued Medicine for Pain Management</a></h3>
          <p>This pioneering technology reduces the active dosage of opioids or other pain medications through a sensory cue, harnessing the placebo effect to help alleviate pain. By supporting gradual reduction of medication, this innovation addresses opioid addiction risks and could transform pain management.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/devgandhi7/Callix-Research-/main/IMG_3643.jpg" alt="Transnasal Device for Infection Prevention">
          <h3 class="device-heading"><a href="https://www.callixresearch.com/innovations/transnasal-device-for-infection-prevention">Transnasal Device for Infection Prevention</a></h3>
          <p>Our patent-pending transnasal device offers a novel, non-invasive method to reduce respiratory infection risks. This device targets pathogens in the nasal passages, providing antimicrobial benefits and a user-friendly design ideal for high-risk environments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/devgandhi7/Callix-Research-/main/IMG_3661.jpg" alt="Neuro-Olfactory Device for Odor-Triggered Prevention">
          <h3 class="device-heading"><a href="https://www.callixresearch.com/innovations/neuro-olfactory-triggered-illness-treatment">Neuro-Olfactory Device for Odor-Triggered Prevention</a></h3>
          <p>With our patented aerosolized nasal spray, we aim to prevent odor-triggered migraines and nausea without the use of preservatives. This product, based on Generally Recognized as Safe (GRAS) ingredients, offers significant potential for over-the-counter or prescription use to mitigate triggers for migraines and other neuro-olfactory illnesses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
